#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_mushrooms/huge.lua:49
msgid ""
"This decorative block is like a huge mushroom stem, but with the stem "
"texture on all sides."
msgstr ""
"Dekorativní blok, podobný jako stonek houby, ale s texturou na všech "
"stranách."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_mushrooms/huge.lua:107
msgid ""
"By placing huge mushroom blocks of the same species next to each other, the "
"sides that touch each other will turn into pores permanently."
msgstr ""
"Když vedle sebe položíte bloky obřích hub stejného druhu, strany, které se "
"vzájemně dotýkají, se trvale promění v póry."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_mushrooms/huge.lua:166
msgid ""
"Huge red mushroom blocks are the cap parts of huge red mushrooms. It "
"consists of a red skin and can have pores on each of its sides."
msgstr ""
"Muchomůrkové blokyjsou části klobouků muchomůrek. Skládá se z červené slupky "
"a pórů."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_mushrooms/huge.lua:167
msgid "The stem part of a huge red mushroom."
msgstr "Stonek obrovské červené houby."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_mushrooms/huge.lua:168
msgid "Huge Red Mushroom Block"
msgstr "Obrovský červený houbový blok"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_mushrooms/huge.lua:168
msgid "Huge Red Mushroom Stem"
msgstr "Stonek velké červené houby"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_mushrooms/huge.lua:168
msgid "Huge Red Mushroom All-Faces Stem"
msgstr "všestraný stonek velké červené houby"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_mushrooms/huge.lua:171
msgid ""
"Huge brown mushroom blocks are the cap parts of huge brown mushrooms. It "
"consists of a brown skin and can have pores on each of its sides."
msgstr ""

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_mushrooms/huge.lua:172
msgid "The stem part of a huge brown mushroom."
msgstr ""

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_mushrooms/huge.lua:173
